{"article_id":"KWUoy6nBGEYaQkby","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"SEOUL/HANOI","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"( ) -","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"South Korea will work with the United States and North Korea","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"to help them reach a denuclearization deal ,","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"South Korean President Moon Jae-in said on Friday ,","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"a day after a U.S.-North Korean summit collapsed over a disagreement on sanctions .","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"The second meeting between U.S. President Donald Trump and North Korean leader Kim Jong Un , in Vietnam , was cut short","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"after they failed to reach a deal on the extent of sanctions relief","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"North Korea would get in exchange for steps","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"to give up its nuclear program .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"Moon has been active in efforts","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"to end confrontation on the Korean peninsula ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"meeting Kim three times last year","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"and trying to facilitate his nuclear negotiations with the United States .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"\" My administration will closely communicate and cooperate with the United States and North Korea","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"so as to help their talks reach a complete settlement by any means , \"","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"Moon said in a speech in Seoul .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"Moon also said","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"Seoul would consult Washington on ways","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"to resume joint projects with North Korea ,","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"including tourism development at Mount Kumgang and the Kaesong industrial complex , both in North Korea .","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"Both the United States and North Korea have said","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"they intend to continue talks ,","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"but have not said","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"when a next round might take place .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"In a move","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"that could encourage more talks ,","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"U.S. officials said on Friday","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"the United States and South Korea are expected to announce","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"that they will not carry out large-scale spring joint military exercises ,","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"replacing them with smaller-scale drills .","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"The allies suspended a number of military drills before and after the first Trump-Kim summit last year","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"to encourage talks with North Korea ,","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"which denounced the exercises as training for invasion .","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"Trump has repeatedly complained about the expense of the exercises","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"and did so again after the Hanoi summit .","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"Trump and Kim first met in Singapore last June","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"and agreed to establish new relations and peace in exchange for a North Korean pledge","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"to work toward complete denuclearization of the Korean peninsula .","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"Trump said","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"two days of talks in Hanoi made good progress","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"but it was important not to rush into a bad deal .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"he had walked away","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"because of unacceptable North Korean demands .","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"\" Basically , they wanted the sanctions lifted in their entirety ,","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"and we couldn ' t do that , \"","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"U.S. Secretary of State Mike Pompeo , in a phone call with China ' s top diplomat Yang Jiechi on Friday , reiterated Washington ' s support","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"for keeping in place U.N. sanctions on North Korea ,","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"they \" remain a central pillar \" of efforts","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"to pressure Pyongyang to denuclearize ,","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"the U.S. State Department said in a statement .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"On Friday , Trump tweeted","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"that the negotiations with Kim were \" very substantive \"","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"and that \" we know what they want","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"and they know what we must have , \"","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"but he gave no other details about any next steps .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"\" Relationship very good ,","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"let ' s see what happens ! \"","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"the post said .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"North Korean Foreign Minister Ri Yong Ho said","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"after Trump left Hanoi","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"that North Korea had sought only a partial lifting of sanctions","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"\" related to people ' s livelihoods","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"and unrelated to military sanctions . \"","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"it offered a realistic proposal","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"involving the dismantling of all of its main nuclear site at Yongbyon ,","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"including plutonium and uranium facilities ,","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"by engineers from both countries .","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"While North Korea ' s official media said","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"Kim and Trump had decided to continue talks ,","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"its Vice Foreign Minister Choe Son Hui has struck a more negative tone ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"telling reporters","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"Kim \" might lose his willingness","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"to pursue a deal \" .","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"South Korean President Moon Jae-in delivers a speech during a ceremony","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"celebrating the 100th anniversary of the March First Independence Movement against Japanese colonial rule ,","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"in central Seoul , South Korea , March 1 , 2019 .","depth":5},{"id":81,"text":"/Kim Hong-Ji","depth":4},{"id":82,"text":"\" It occurs to us that there may not be a need","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"to continue , \"","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"she said ,","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"adding","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"that North Korea had taken \" many steps \"","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"to try to reach a deal .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"\" We ' re doing a lot of thinking , \"","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"she said","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"while adding","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"that the situation would change","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"\"","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"if our demands can be resolved . \"","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"Pompeo told a news conference in Manila","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"the U.S. side was \" anxious to get back to the table","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"so we can continue that conversation","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"that will ultimately lead to peace and stability , better life for the North Korean people , and a lower threat , a denuclearized North Korea . \"","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"And North Korea ' s state news agency was conciliatory ,","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"quoting Kim as expressing gratitude to Trump","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"for putting in efforts","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"to get results","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"and calling their exchanges constructive .","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"It made no mention of the breakdown of the summit .","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"Failure","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"to reach an agreement","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"marks a setback for Trump , a self-styled dealmaker under pressure at home over his ties to Russia and testimony from Michael Cohen , his former lawyer","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"who accused him of breaking the law while in office .","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"While some credited Trump for refusing to be drawn into a bad deal ,","depth":6},{"id":109,"text":"he was criticized for praising Kim ' s leadership","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"and saying","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"he accepted his assertion","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"that he had not been aware of how an American student","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"who died after 17 months a North Korean prison","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"had been treated .","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"On Friday , the parents of Otto Warmbier blamed Kim ' s \" evil regime \" for his death .","depth":7},{"id":116,"text":"The collapse of the summit leaves Kim in possession of what analysts say","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"could be an arsenal of 20 to 60 nuclear warheads ,","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"which ,","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"if fitted to its intercontinental ballistic missiles ,","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"could threaten the U.S. mainland .","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"Trump stressed","depth":6},{"id":122,"text":"that the North Korean leader had agreed to maintain his moratorium on nuclear and ballistic missile tests .","depth":6},{"id":123,"text":"A U.S. State Department official said","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"the North Korean media coverage had been constructive ,","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"indicating","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"both sides felt","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"there was \" ample opportunity \"","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"to continue talks .","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"The U.S. official said","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"North Korea had proposed closing part of its Yongbyon nuclear complex in exchange for lifting \" basically all \" U.N. sanctions","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"except those directly targeting its weapons programs .","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"The U.S. side said","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"\" that wouldn ' t work \" ,","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"he said ,","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"adding","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"that North Korea was unwilling to completely freeze its weapons programs .","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"\" So to give many , many billions of dollars in sanctions relief would in effect put us in a position","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"of subsidizing the ongoing development of weapons of mass destruction , \"","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"said the official ,","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"who spoke on condition of anonymity .","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"The United Nations and the United States ratcheted up sanctions on North Korea","depth":7},{"id":142,"text":"when it conducted repeated nuclear and ballistic missile tests in 2017 .","depth":7},{"id":143,"text":"Washington has demanded North Korea ' s complete , verifiable and irreversible denuclearization","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"before sanctions can be lifted ,","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"a position","depth":8},{"id":146,"text":"Pyongyang has denounced as \" gangster like . \"","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":293,"left":0,"right":292,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":292,"left":227,"right":291,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":227,"left":223,"right":226,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":223,"left":184,"right":222,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":184,"left":155,"right":183,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":151,"right":154,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":1,"right":150,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":150,"left":148,"right":149,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":6,"right":153,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":7,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"